data.description: First time home buyers or Investors.  This 2 story town house in the heart of Merritt Island,  with 2 bedroom 1 bath,  Jack and Jill sinks up stairs, with a large master suite and 2nd bedroom. 1/2 bath downstairs, Home also features screened patio off the kitchen with a beautiful private garden area. This townhome has a indoor washer and dryer hook up.  What a great opportunity in a development with a pool.  Low maintenance fee.  Will not last long.
